headline: Medtronic (MDT) Expands MiniMed System To Type 2 Diabetes With FDA Approvals
summary: Medtronic (MDT) recently achieved significant FDA regulatory milestones with its MiniMed™ 780G system, notably enhancing its diabetes management capabilities. This advancement, along with Medtronic's consistent financial performance—evident in stable earnings and a 48-year streak of increasing dividends—aligned with an upward trend in tech stocks, contributed to the company's 9% share price gain last quarter.
